<p>
  <span class="nym">Opportune</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Middle French</span> <i>opportun</i> 'suitable, fitting', a derivative of <span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>opportunus</i> 'fit, suitable, convenient, timely'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of an 8th C French saint.</p>
</div>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>An unusual example of a virtue name outside of England.</p>
</div>
  


